OL,3,CCombining blood test with AI could
OL,4,Cprovide 'more accurate' sepsis
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FCombining artificial intelligence (AI)
OL,8,Fwith a simple blood test could help
OL,9,Fdiagnose sepsis faster and single out
OL,10,Fpatients at the highest risk of severe
OL,11,Fcomplications from the infection, a
OL,12,Fstudy has suggested.
OL,14,FThe approach could save lives,
OL,15,Faccording to Swedish researchers, who
OL,16,Fcombined the unique molecular
OL,17,Fsignature of sepsis with machine-
OL,18,Flearning to predict a person's risk of
OL,19,Forgan failure and death.
