OL,7,FSepsis is life-threatening and,
OL,8,Faccounting for about 50,000 deaths
OL,9,Feach year in the UK.
OL,11,FDr Lisa Mellhammar, of Lund University
OL,12,Fin Sweden, said it's vital that
OL,13,Fpatients with suspected sepsis are
OL,14,Fidentified prior to the onset of organ
OL,15,Ffailure.J"Given the and the fact that
OL,16,Fsepsis kills millions of people around
OL,17,Fthe world every year, there is an
OL,18,Furgent demand for an alternative
OL,19,Fapproach," she said.
