OL,7,FShe added that a blood test, combined
OL,8,Fwith a personalised risk model, "has
OL,9,Fthe potential to save lives by
OL,10,Fproviding and determining who may go
OL,11,Fon to develop more severe clinical
OL,12,Fmanifestations".
OL,14,FResearchers looked at 1,364 plasma
OL,15,Fsamples of adults admitted to the
OL,16,Femergency department at Skane
OL,17,FUniversity with suspected sepsis
OL,18,Fbetween September 2016 and March 2023.
OL,20,FOf the 1,073 patients with an
OL,21,Finfection, some 913 had sepsis.
