OL,12,FThe team then analysed proteins
OL,13,Fassociated with the body's immune
OL,14,Fresponse to sepsis to see if there was
OL,15,Fa pattern.
OL,17,FThey created molecular signatures from
OL,18,Ftheir analysis, which was used to
OL,19,Ftrain an AI model to predict who was
OL,20,Flikely to go into septic shock.
