OL,7,FPatients were classified as low,
OL,8,Fmedium and high risk of developing
OL,9,Fseptic shock, with the technology able
OL,10,Fto show how increasing risk was
OL,11,Fassociated with a higher rate of death.
OL,13,FDr Adam Linder, also of Lund
OL,14,FUniversity, said it's difficult to,
OL,15,Fwho will recover, and who will have
OL,16,Fpoor outcomes.
