OL,7,F"We urgently need better ways to
OL,8,Funderstand sepsis at the molecular
OL,9,Flevel so we can classify according to
OL,10,Fthe clinical manifestations of their
OL,11,Fillness and identify high-risk
OL,12,Fpatients and develop more effective
OL,13,Ftreatments."
OL,15,FResearchers also identified panels of
OL,16,Fproteins that predicted dysfunction in
OL,17,Fsix different organ types, including
OL,18,Fthe heart, liver and kidneys.
