OL,7,FThey then classified patients into
OL,8,Ffive risk categories based on the
OL,9,Fprobability of them having organ
OL,10,Fdysfunction and infection, and their
OL,11,Frisk of dying.JThe findings of the
OL,12,Fstudy will be presented at the
OL,13,FEuropean Congress of Clinical
OL,14,FMicrobiology and Infectious Diseases
OL,15,Fin Barcelona at the end of April.
OL,17,FIt comes as NHS England prepares from
OL,18,Fnext month.
