OL,7,FThe escalation process is designed to
OL,8,Fformalise access to a critical care
OL,9,Fteam for a second opinion if and they
OL,10,For their family feels they are not
OL,11,Fgetting the care needed.
OL,13,FMartha Mills, 13, died in 2021 after
OL,14,Fdeveloping sepsis from a pancreatic
OL,15,Finjury she suffered after falling off
OL,16,Fher bike.
OL,18,FHer parents, Merope Mills and Paul
OL,19,FLaity, raised concerns about their
OL,20,Fdaughter's health a number of times
OL,21,Fbut these were brushed aside.
